---
/* Componente: ¿Por Qué Elegirnos? */
/* SEO: H2 correcto, sin H3 innecesarios */
---

<section
  class="py-20"
  style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, hsl(0 0% 100%) 0%, hsl(210 30% 98%) 100%);"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Título de sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] mb-4">
        ¿Por Qué Elegirnos?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Somos tu mejor opción porque conectamos tu necesidad con el profesional ideal:
        calificado, con experiencia y con certificación verificable.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de beneficios -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Beneficio 1 -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Pago directo al profesional, finalizando turno
            </p>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Precios justos para ti y dignidad laboral para el personal de enfermería.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 2 -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
              <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22"/>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Hasta 50% más económico
            </p>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Comparado con agencias tradicionales, sin sacrificar calidad.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 3 -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Totalmente legal
            </p>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Profesionales registrados ante el Ministerio de Salud.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 4 -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Atención personalizada
            </p>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Jornadas de 8 o 12 horas según tus necesidades reales.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 5 -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
              <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"/>
              <polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Especializados en post-cirugía
            </p>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Experiencia en recuperación postoperatoria y pacientes internacionales.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 6 -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
              <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.29 1.51 4.04 3 5.5l7 7Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Compromiso ético
            </p>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Prioridad al bienestar humano por encima de intereses comerciales.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
